Deployment on Vercel
Automatic Git Integration: Push to GitHub triggers deployment

Serverless Functions: API routes handled by Vercel Functions

Global CDN: Assets served from edge locations worldwide

Automatic HTTPS: SSL certificates provisioned automatically
